{{Infobox television | show_name = CNN Business Traveller | image = CNN_Business_Traveller_logo.png | image_size = | image_alt = | caption = | genre = [[Business]], [[travel]] | creator = | writer = | director = | presenter = [[Richard Quest]] | theme_music_composer = | executive_producer = | producer = | editor = | location = Varies | camera = [[Multiple-camera setup]] | runtime = 30 minutes {{small|({{tooltip|inc.|including}} adverts)}} | channel = [[CNN International]] | first_run = | first_aired = 2002 | last_aired = present | preceded_by = | related = | website = http://edition.cnn.com/specials/travel/business-traveller }} '''CNN Business Traveller''' is a monthly television program on [[CNN International]] hosted by [[Richard Quest]].
The program was launched in 2002<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2009/jun/22/richard-quest-cnn-means-business|title='I can't turn the clock back' |work=The Guardian|date=22 June 2009|accessdate=18 June 2016|first=Gareth|last=McLean}}</ref> and the program investigates various topics related to business related travel, including [[airlines]], [[airport lounge]]s, [[frequent-flyer program]]s, hotels and the travelling lifestyle.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.btnews.co.uk/article/9848|title=Article from BTNews 1 FEBRUARY 2016|date=1 February 2016|accessdate=18 June 2016|work=BTN}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hmhhotelgroup.com/pressandmedia/article/248|title=HMH CEO LAURENT A. VOIVENEL ON THE CNN BUSINESS TRAVELLER SHOW|work=HMH Hotel Group|accessdate=18 June 2016}}</ref>
James Williams was also a producer and occasional presenter on the program, before being given his own CNN program in 2016 titled ''[[In 24 Hours]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tvtonight.com.au/2016/03/dream-job-for-cnns-james-williams.html|title=Dream job for CNN’s James Williams|work=[[TV Tonight]]|first=David|last=Knox|date=1 March 2016|accessdate=18 June 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://enter.hermesawards.com/entry/cnn-business-traveller-concur-interview/|title=CNN Business Traveller Concur Interview|work=Grayling|accessdate=18 June 2016|dead-url=no|archivedate=18 June 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160618024135/https://enter.hermesawards.com/entry/cnn-business-traveller-concur-interview/}}</ref>
